This paper discusses the integration of machine learning and context aware computing on the Android platform, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also focuses on providing higher utility to users, which can be related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the proactive gauging of users' requirements, which can be related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Lastly, the paper discusses the use of association rules, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
